these rude creatures
women!
What's that scar on
your breast, brigadier?
Brig.
Slide down your nictitating membrane,
mi-boy, and don't be too observing! Here goes!
Hup!
(The brigadier rushes into the surf, takes a
stitch through three frills of the island's shirt, and rises
